/**
 * Generates the Capital One Phone Banking documentation in Markdown format.
 * @returns {string} - The complete Markdown string for Capital One Phone Banking.
 */
function generateCapitalOnePhoneBankingMarkdown() {
  return `
# Capital One Phone Banking

## Introduction

Capital One offers a robust phone banking system that allows customers to manage their accounts easily and securely over the phone.

<!-- Tip Callout -->
<div style="border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0;">
    <strong>Tip:</strong> Always keep your account information secure and do not share it over the phone.
</div>

## Key Features

- **Account Management**: Check balances, view transactions, and manage account settings.
- **Payments**: Make payments directly from your phone.
- **Customer Support**: Speak with a representative for assistance with your account.
- **Fraud Alerts**: Report suspicious activity immediately.

<!-- Note Callout -->
<div style="border-left: 4px solid #2196F3; background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0;">
    <strong>Note:</strong> The Capital One mobile app also allows you to manage your accounts on the go, including viewing statements and making payments.
</div>

## How to Access

To access Capital One's phone banking services, call their customer service number at **1-800-655-2265**. Follow the prompts to navigate through the system.

<!-- Warning Callout -->
<div style="border-left: 4px solid #f44336; background-color: #ffebee; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0;">
    <strong>Warning:</strong> Never provide your PIN or password to anyone over the phone. If you suspect fraud, report it immediately.
</div>

## Additional Features

### Mobile App Integration
The Capital One mobile app enhances your banking experience by allowing you to:
- View statements and transaction history.
- Make payments and transfer funds.
- Lock and unlock credit cards in case of loss or theft.

<!-- Did You Know Callout -->
<div style="border-left: 4px solid #FF9800; background-color: #fff3e0; padding: 10px; margin: 10px 0;">
    <strong>Did You Know?</strong> You can use the app to set up virtual cards for online shopping, providing an extra layer of security by not exposing your actual card number.
</div>

## Notes

- Ensure you have your account information ready when calling.
- Phone banking is available **24/7** for your convenience.
`;
